{"tid":1010142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"賀歲盃費托之追星犯眾憎","createTime":"2019-02-05T17:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T04:48:17.000Z","uid":100950,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b046165db1f6dc15a653cc993c4e9fab8b499c55","tid":1010142,"uid":100950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"【賀歲盃】費托賽後返酒店　球迷欲索簽名與酒店職員爭執　警列糾紛處理<br />\n <br />\n今日賀歲盃比賽結束後，鳥栖砂岩球隊返回酒店時，陣中球星費蘭度托利斯未有與在場30、40名球迷簽名，直接回酒店房休息。現場消息指，晚上9時許，其中兩名球迷進入酒店報稱訂房，但拒絕向酒店職員提供個人資料，並繼續在酒店不同樓層流連，欲等候球星簽名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n費托嚟咗香港幾日就肆虐咗幾日 唔知有幾多守規矩規矩嘅巴打比佢哋搞到簽唔到名影唔到相 有冇其他苦主出嚟講下 聽講佢哋已經唔係第一次 每逢有球星嚟都會搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f365fdda41b3fff3c41ebb626f8794cf52850f","tid":1010142,"uid":100950,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T17:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mZnxAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mZnxAW.png&h=1131402d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WX6X5VX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWX6X5VX.png&h=09540ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48Y7JHD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48Y7JHD.png&h=26a58d48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQpVSAY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuQpVSAY.png&h=f711db6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipQFjfZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FipQFjfZ.png&h=0425f67d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"